{"tid":1763333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[民間記者會] 催淚毒煙 禍延我城 問卷調查","createTime":"2019-11-30T08:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T14:23:16.000Z","uid":325953,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"6998a4efff5544d2fb1e7f9e135b5e889037e76b","tid":1763333,"uid":325953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:52:19.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MfDewEF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMfDewEF.jpg&h=706f93c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n得返唔夠48小時炸 但竟然得7000人做左問卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，喺唔喺想政府講催淚煙影響得7000人啊，我地都唔信，所以大家一齊做，做完就叫人做。<br />\n民間記者會第六次民間調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThe 6th Citizens' Press Conference Survey</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">催淚毒煙 禍延我城<br />\nTear Gas are Poisoning Our City<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.citizenspc.org/survey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizenspc.org%2Fsurvey&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipfx%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=38fcaa54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.citizenspc.org/survey</a><br />\n問卷截止時間為<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">12月1日(星期日)晚上8時</span></em></span></div><br />\n<br />\n今次調查唔再喺一日限定，喺一連三日，由依家去到12月1日，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔理你喺多數派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、泛民主派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、少數派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、親中派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定喺Mon Po狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、<span style=\"color: purple;\">催淚毒煙對你嘅影響一定有。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>所以入黎幫手做份問卷。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋今次加咗仔女部分，有小朋友嘅手足都可以填埋㗎！！<br />\n<br />\n再一次多謝大家對民間記者會嘅支持！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164ab20b100bf5ab13b9a21e76ab9ed5a6f17bb2","tid":1763333,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8cd9712328e7defec6ac3eaf58c03848b646ff","tid":1763333,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:53:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fce7b67e46d10540aab58f150e7a655c2324e6d","tid":1763333,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5f44d32b16c69836d80c12ab3d6353636f7f4c","tid":1763333,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717af8065b3c5aaa0add1b2bd32e49a25ee5bebc","tid":1763333,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:54:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6af4c9fa238e0226b805c3ae4dfde2ee175c03d7","tid":1763333,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmo