ass=\"hkgmoji\" />，喺唔喺想政府講催淚煙影響得7000人啊，我地都唔信，所以大家一齊做，做完就叫人做。<br />\n民間記者會第六次民間調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThe 6th Citizens' Press Conference Survey</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">催淚毒煙 禍延我城<br />\nTear Gas are Poisoning Our City<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.citizenspc.org/survey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizenspc.org%2Fsurvey&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipfx%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=38fcaa54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.citizenspc.org/survey</a><br />\n問卷截止時間為<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">12月1日(星期日)晚上8時</span></em></span></div><br />\n<br />\n今次調查唔再喺一日限定，喺一連三日，由依家去到12月1日，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔理你喺多數派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、泛民主派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、少數派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、親中派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定喺Mon Po狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、<span style=\"color: purple;\">催淚毒煙對你嘅影響一定有。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>所以入黎幫手做份問卷。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋今次加咗仔女部分，有小朋友嘅手足都可以填埋㗎！！<br />\n<br />\n再一次多謝大家對民間記者會嘅支持！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T09:30:30.000Z","msg":"催淚水劑算唔算催淚煙？"},{"pid":"c01954ac0cf657bc54ece1f6eb6d07d9c320cdcc","tid":1763333,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d7617579102f1f2844c70e1ee398955f13270b","tid":1763333,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b3755eeacde3cea35d2ad3e97d8ac2a218185f","tid":1763333,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T09:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d5cd910845e33a9bf650e8c19cbb7eee08c40d","tid":1763333,"uid":325953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e01a651043f45f887aeaddbc5ea3053258ee0b1a","tid":1763333,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"075b6708f97f44159d414a8281afc18e0ece02f4","tid":1763333,"uid":325953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f835fe4998f784931980f95d0e48998dfcb377a","tid":1763333,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T09:14:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"係咪個張人體圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地想仔細分"},"cited